## SRC\_ATOP\_I variable

Porter-Duff operator for packed ints. The source that overlaps the destination is composited with the destination.

[porterDuff](./porter-duff.porterduff.md)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
SRC_ATOP_I: (a: number, b: number) => number
```
